column3: the streaming on the web is not so smooth,it paused occasionlly
column4:
I try to add a video file ,but the streaming on the web is not so smooth,it paused occasionlly and it will be slower than the origin video.
I've checked the source code and try to change some parameter (frameskip, framerate, etc), but the result is all the same.Then I wonder if it because my computer is a little bit old ,so I run it on a server(intel i7,  nvidea 1080 && 64G RAM),but it's still not change.
I still use the xuggle not  Humble-Video, so is it the reason?
So could you please tell me how can I make the streaming more fluid.
I'm a begginner of storm ,from China. I would appreciate it if you can reply.
